name: DrugOverdoseAndPoisoningNonOpioidOtherDrugSNOMED
title: Drug Overdose and Poisoning [Non opioid] [Other Drug] (SNOMED)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses or problems that represent that the patient has non-opioid drug overdose or poisoning from other drugs regardless of the clinical presentation of the condition),(Data Element Scope: Diagnoses or problems documented in a clinical record.),(Inclusion Criteria: Non-opioid psychotropic drugs),(Exclusion Criteria: stimulants, depressants, cannabinoids, hallucinogens, analgesics)
